ke":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T02:54:46.000Z","msg":"陳日君樞機曾經屌過佢對中國天主教徒處境置之不顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:36:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a78250bffc0594e58261f2bccf364a005d10a40","tid":2491354,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"教宗行出嚟話佢無罪就得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b3c744287d3babf4afd9315c2e2f8109442b34","tid":2491354,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T04:24:57.000Z","msg":"查埋佢有冇搞幻幻"},{"pid":"0840dc0d4885afefea3ba8aec05f85a01728a763","tid":2491354,"uid":394702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3098a2def29287510421ca977c3d82cc79410dd9","tid":2491354,"uid":56321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T05:52:53.000Z","msg":"腐敗不堪，根本教會歷史一直都發生不道德嘅事件"},{"pid":"57ce8dab8cde245439a87f74f4828d0637da3582","tid":2491354,"uid":196671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T07:51:48.000Z","msg":"帕洛琳條奶共走狗都有今日啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cheer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}